{"tid":934584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 華為危機】葉劉話會轉用華為手機","createTime":"2018-12-09T11:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T06:02:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"059bc171c6687782def156f0b2387138eaed0444","tid":934584,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T11:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181209/large/1544352837_65e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181209%2Flarge%2F1544352837_65e1.png&h=19ebb5c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特區政府至今仍未有回應，在加拿大被捕的華為集團副董事長孟晚舟，為何持有3本特區護照。多個疑團未解下，政務司司長張建宗今日（9日）出席公開活動時，被問到孟晚舟事件時，封口沒有回應。而曾任入境處處長及保安局局長的行會成員、新民黨主席葉劉淑儀則指，現時資料不足以判斷孟，為何曾獲發3本特區護照，亦不清楚她是否同時持有相關護照，但指孟若主動求助，香港入境處一定提供協助。至於被問到會否呼籲市民多用國貨時，葉劉稱不會作此呼籲，但自己會改用華為手機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181209/59010684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59010684&d=8S8G0peBvkyZaqVbO4V6CghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b4cb823c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59010684&h=187e74b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181209/59010684</a>"},{"pid":"8ff155caddf84f15333625a3022c802ed98b06f1","tid":934584,"uid":12754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T11:32:19.000Z","msg":"姊妹？"},{"pid":"31d6d76a6c12ad473d12d0ebf9a270425c5a9a03","tid":934584,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"會唔會將派$4000改做 派 華為手機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5db6b928f80b0b4f8a50f7066bd6b8a05514aa","tid":934584,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"31d6d76a6c12ad473d12d0ebf9a270425c5a9a0